snippet.title: Elon Musk and Michael Saylor Twitter Scam ! Beware ! (Clip from episode 25-11-2021)
snippet.description:
There are Scammers promoting an "Elon Musk" twitter scam and a "Michael Saylor" crypto scam, be very careful what you click on and who you trust your crypto on twitter and telegram
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Time Frames:
0:00 Elon Musk Twitter Scam
1:56  Michael Saylor Twitter Scam
3:06  Telegram Scams

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Long Description:  Twitter Scams are very popular and there are a lot of money to be made, in the latest Micahel Saylor twitter crypto scam, bad actors successfully have stolen 5 million dollars already. There is one Elon Musk twitter scam going on but not so successful. Also be careful of hacks that may be attempted on high profile twitter accounts and also telegram fake accounts and members
